Description_lang: Your healing spells have a chance to trigger Power of the Waves. Power of the Waves travels from you to  an injured ally over $209842d. When triggered, it pops, granting $209843s1 healing to all allies within 5 yards. Other allies may touch Azshara's Boon to activate this effect.
